WEBVTT

00:00:56.491 --> 00:01:01.382
because architecture, at the end,
is the art of making buildings.

00:01:01.910 --> 00:01:06.487
Architecture is the art of making
shelter for human beings.

00:01:07.370 --> 00:01:08.520
Period.

00:01:08.878 --> 00:01:10.745
And this is not easy at all.

00:01:11.060 --> 00:01:12.210
It's amazing.

00:01:13.038 --> 00:01:14.188
Look at this.

00:01:15.427 --> 00:01:17.482
Here we are in London,

00:01:17.506 --> 00:01:22.115
at the top of the Shard of Glass.

00:01:23.309 --> 00:01:26.964
This is a building
we completed a few years ago.

00:01:26.988 --> 00:01:32.709
Those people are well-trained workers,